    "description": "远在卡洛斯大战之前，你和你的深渊领主同伴被你的邪恶导师门德卓斯（一直由桀骜不驯的Richard Ridings配音）带着，在埃特中旅游。在暴风雨来临前的宁静，让深渊领主没有什么可以做……除了亲自打理自己的宠物动物园！踏入宠物地下城的休闲领域：发现，试验，释放你梦想中的地下城！<br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542160/extras/6e68a677e0ef590b25ebaed6e1066fa5.avif?t=1743526218\" width=600 height=175 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>建造你梦想中的地下城</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542160/extras/1-_Building.JPG?t=1743526218\" /></span><br>8个等级的沙箱风格战役，特别为宠物地下城而设计的，比起主游戏更为休闲。达到目标分数就可以前进至下一等级，追逐奖励目标，或是简单地陶醉在你的梦中。（现在两个等级免费开放）<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与你的敌人玩耍</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542160/extras/2-_Toybox.JPG?t=1743526218\" /></span><br>抓住英雄，设置他们的力量，然后透过新的玩具盒子房间将他们丢在地图上的任何位置。使用生成功能，召唤一个或是无限的波敌人，来让你的地下城按你的心意发展。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>使用神模式</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542160/extras/5651169b04496b017c168c28ac836eb7.poster.avif?t=1743526218\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542160/extras/5651169b04496b017c168c28ac836eb7.webm?t=1743526218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542160/extras/5651169b04496b017c168c28ac836eb7.mp4?t=1743526218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>完成宠物地下城来解锁神模式：重新设计等级或是凭空生成战斗单位-全部实时！到底你会创造出什么样的可笑场景呢？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>发现与解锁</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542160/extras/20ebbb93227b3acf820f295dbf69ca59.poster.avif?t=17